Confined.description: Confined was a horror game being developed by DemonKingSwarn but eventually he stopped working on it because he started getting weary of it.

ManagerCEO.description: Nikhil Malankar gave the ownership of this game to DemonKingSwarn who then gave it to Aayush who then killed the game out of his lack of interest.

URI.description: One of the first group projects of Aayush(cloudy) at GameOH. Later got killed due to skill issue. I really liked its aesthetics, 2D lights - good old days of working in 2D.

Avoid - Reborn.description: Full version of Aayush's popular game - Avoid. Avoid also happens to be his first published game in Brackeys game jam.
